    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. While the car does start, the engine has a persistent knock and the transmission struggles to engage properly, often slipping during gear changes. The body has several significant dents and the paint is peeling in multiple areas, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It will likely require a tow to its next destination and significant repairs before it can be considered roadworthy.",
