    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it\u2019s honestly in such solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, making it the perfect dependable daily driver for its next owner. It still looks great and drives smoothly\u2014I'm really going to miss it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
