      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated mill features individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced subframe and updated bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, providing the communicative steering and lateral stability characteristic of the marque. While displaying minor aesthetic patina commensurate with its age, the drivetrain and cooling system have been meticulously sorted for peak operational performance.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. No major issues.",
      "price": 36500.0,
