    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous care. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and pristine; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned to prevent cracking, and every electronic component\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a full brake inspection completed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. While there is very light curbing on the rear passenger wheel, the overall presentation is sharp and professional. This is a reliable, well-documented vehicle perfect for someone who values mechanical integrity and a clean aesthetic.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
